  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements: </strong>Aberrant, daemon, demon, or devil subtype or the undead appearance evolution; summoner level 7th.</p>\n<p>One of the eidolon’s natural weapons carries a disease chosen from the following list:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bubonic plague,</li>\n<li>filth fever,</li>\n<li>leprosy,</li>\n<li>red ache, or</li>\n<li>shakes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Each hit forces a saving throw against the disease’s normal effects. The disease has no onset, however. The save DC equals 10 + 1/2 the eidolon’s Hit Dice + the eidolon’s Constitution modifier. The eidolon can expose a creature to its disease no more than once per round.</p>\n<p>By spending 2 additional evolution points, you can instead choose the following additional diseases:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>demon fever (only if the eidolon has the demon subtype),</li>\n<li>devil chills (only if the eidolon has the devil subtype), or</li>\n<li>slimy doom.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>",
